hopobject.body: Could I borrow your phone, please? careplus.wholehealthmd.com Hollywood is teeming with famous same-sex couples - some more open than others. From public declarations of love to dates out of the limelight, check out the stars who have found romance with that special someone ... "Modern Family" star Jesse Tyler Ferguson is a married man! The actor said "I do" on July 20, 2013 to longtime love Justin Mikita in a Manhattan ceremony officiated by playwright Tony Kushner, the actor's rep confirmed to People magazine. Ferguson, 37, and Mikita, 27, got engaged in September of last year, after dating for nearly two years.
